WEBVTT

00:13:30.640 --> 00:13:32.936
Na kraju događaja ove godine,

00:13:32.960 --> 00:13:36.640
jedna od naših mladih,
divnih tinejdžerki,

00:13:37.680 --> 00:13:40.000
Caitlin, rekla je svojoj mami,

00:13:41.640 --> 00:13:44.456
"To je bila najbolja
noć mog života."

00:13:44.480 --> 00:13:46.856
I upravo to je poanta,

00:13:46.880 --> 00:13:50.616
uhvatiti najbolje dane i noći,

00:13:50.640 --> 00:13:52.720
ukinuti ograničenja,

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:55.656
imati zadani odgovor "da"

00:13:55.680 --> 00:13:58.720
i zadano pitanje "Zašto ne?"

00:13:59.800 --> 00:14:02.296
Na kraju krajeva život je prekratak,